Cambodia: An attempted invasion of Vietnam was defeated.
China:
Song established a standing navy headquartered at Dinghai in modern Dinghai District.
A fire destroyed some thirteen thousand homes in the Song capital Lin'an City.
Estonia: Prince Vsevolod of Novgorod is defeated by Estonians of Vaiga county.
Russia: Mstislav died. His brother Yaropolk II followed him as prince of Kiev.
